27
00:02:26.600 --> 00:02:27.820
Here are my disclosures.

28
00:02:29.540 --> 00:02:33.380
So a key takeaway point is that intraperitoneal mesothelin-targeted

29
00:02:33.400 --> 00:02:35.180
CAR T cell administration was safe.

30
00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:39.950
CAR T persistence was noted in the peripheral blood beyond

