32
00:02:41.880 --> 00:02:44.970
Antitumor activity in mesothelin-positive esophageal gastric

33
00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:48.670
adenocarcinoma was limited, and this is likely reflecting the

34
00:02:48.700 --> 00:02:50.470
heterogeneous target expression.

35
00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:54.860
Given the safety data that we observed and the higher level of mesothelin

36
00:02:54.870 --> 00:02:58.800
expression in peritoneal mesothelioma, we are amending the

37
00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:00.720
