78
00:05:27.700 --> 00:05:30.900
These patients were monitored for at least two days inpatient and subsequently

79
00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:32.560
discharged to outpatient follow-up.

80
00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:37.890
Here we have the primary objectives, again, as mentioned earlier, and we have the

81
00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:41.560
dose escalation scheme based on the continual reassessment method.

82
00:05:42.030 --> 00:05:45.860
And we started at dose level two with dose of three times ten to power six

83
00:05:45.900 --> 00:05:46.860
cells per kilogram.

84
00:05:48.580 --> 00:05:52.460
We screened 54 patients, and of these, 19 were positive

85
00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:56.700
and eligible for enrollment. And to date, we have treated seven patients with

86
00:05:56.780 --> 00:06:00.684
IP-administered CAR.Here we have the baseline

