97
00:06:36.324 --> 00:06:39.884
We can see the best response was stable disease in several patients,

98
00:06:40.604 --> 00:06:44.524
and progression-free survival as stated, which I will go into greater detail in a

99
00:06:44.584 --> 00:06:45.244
