487
00:30:06.192 --> 00:30:09.772
better persistence and activation with these edited TIL, and

488
00:30:09.812 --> 00:30:13.372
therefore, we specifically chose a dose of one to 10 billion

489
00:30:13.432 --> 00:30:15.982
TIL to be used for this

