00:31:18.024 --> 00:31:21.604
Patients were treated with standard doses of lymph

508
00:31:21.624 --> 00:31:25.584
depletion, including cyclophosphamide, 60 milligram per kilogram for two days,

509
00:31:26.104 --> 00:31:29.684
and fludarabine, 25 milligrams per meter square for five days,

510
00:31:29.864 --> 00:31:33.824
followed by a single KSQ001EX infusion, and then

511
00:31:33.864 --> 00:31:37.284
up to six doses of high-dose IL-2 just for the cohort two patients.

512
00:31:37.884 --> 00:31:41.524
DLT assessment period was 28 days, and then patients were followed

513
00:31:41.984 --> 00:31:44.904
routinely for imaging for resist response.

514
00:31:46.904 --> 00:31:50.824
This manufacturing is called the EXPRESS program,

515
00:31:50.884 --> 00:31:54.864
which is a proprietary engineered manufacturing process,

516
00:31:55.004 --> 00:31:57.844
which is a 22-day PBMC feeder-free

517
00:31:58.604 --> 00:32:02.464
environment. TIL are extracted from the tumor

518
00:32:02.524 --> 00:32:06.244
starting material in 11 days or less, followed by CRISPR-Cas9

519
00:32:06.284 --> 00:32:09.984
engineering, and then another 11 days or less for TIL expansion.

520
00:32:10.464 --> 00:32:14.344
This leads to drug product that is highly

521
00:32:14.404 --> 00:32:17.944
efficient in terms of the CRISPR editing, 95%,

522
00:32:18.524 --> 00:32:21.624
and the infusion product is predominantly a CD8,

523
00:32:21.724 --> 00:32:24.484
CD27 positive young TIL phenotype.

524
00:32:25.724 --> 00:32:28.884
Further details about this novel manufacturing can be seen in the poster

525
00:32:28.893 --> 00:32:30.004
presentation tomorrow.

526
00:32:31.314 --> 00:32:34.023
A total of 15 patients underwent tumor harvest.

527
00:32:34.224 --> 00:32:38.024
There were two manufacturing failures and three patients that generated

528
00:32:38.124 --> 00:32:41.884
less than a billion cells, with two of those three patients that were able to be

529
00:32:41.944 --> 00:32:45.404
treated. So a total of 12 patients were included in the safety

530
00:32:45.444 --> 00:32:48.844
analysis. Median age was 46.5 years.

531
00:32:49.204 --> 00:32:51.174
Most patients had BRAF mutations, and

532
00:32:52.004 --> 00:32:55.524
median previous lines of therapy were two, with a range of one to five.

533
00:32:56.264 --> 00:32:59.844
Forty-two percent of patients had elevated LDH, and the median

534
00:32:59.884 --> 00:33:03.504
KSQ001EX cell dose was 5.25 billion

535
00:33:03.604 --> 00:33:03.964
cells.

536
00:33:06.004 --> 00:33:09.324
This regimen was well-tolerated with really majority of

537
00:33:09.364 --> 00:33:12.524
toxicities related to the effects of the lymph depleting

538
00:33:12.604 --> 00:33:16.184
chemotherapy. There was no dose limiting toxicities, there was no

539
00:33:16.304 --> 00:33:20.284
CRS, ICANS, or any obvious SOX1 specific toxicities,

540
00:33:20.354 --> 00:33:21.684
and no Grade 5 events.

541
00:33:23.344 --> 00:33:27.324
Here we see the efficacy for the 10 patients that were treated between one and 10

