00:33:27.364 --> 00:33:29.333
billion TILs. The first

543
00:33:30.224 --> 00:33:34.024
row shows the cell dose, second, number of IL-2 doses specific to

544
00:33:34.084 --> 00:33:38.014
the cohort two patients, and then we see the waterfall plot of response and

