00:34:51.944 --> 00:34:55.685
Here we see a case study of a patient who received 8.4

566
00:34:55.705 --> 00:34:59.034
billion TIL and had prolonged stable disease for over 12 months.

567
00:34:59.784 --> 00:35:01.984
We see in orange the

568
00:35:02.024 --> 00:35:05.664
KSQ001EX over time with persistence out to

