583
00:35:54.204 --> 00:35:57.764
So to conclude, KSQ001EX is a

584
00:35:57.804 --> 00:36:00.524
CRISPR-edited SOX1-inactivated TIL.

585
00:36:01.164 --> 00:36:05.144
This manufacturing leads to a favorable drug product enriched

586
00:36:05.184 --> 00:36:08.574
