00:36:23.264 --> 00:36:27.084
the median cell dose. We do see ability of these cells to

592
00:36:27.104 --> 00:36:30.744
expand and persist in the blood over time, with or without

593
00:36:30.824 --> 00:36:34.584
IL-2, and we can see that these cells have the ability to infiltrate the

594
00:36:34.624 --> 00:36:38.524
tumor and remodulate the tumor microenvironment into a CD8 positive

595
00:36:38.584 --> 00:36:41.952
cytotoxic state.This current clinical trial has

