00:40:51.172 --> 00:40:55.152
And the key question with this novel agent was whether

667
00:40:55.172 --> 00:40:58.452
or not it resulted in durable responses

668
00:40:59.252 --> 00:41:03.152
due to this non-specific recruitment of T-cells in the

669
00:41:03.172 --> 00:41:04.372
