00:47:27.232 --> 00:47:30.952
And then finally, if you look at the ctDNA molecular response criteria, you can

775
00:47:31.072 --> 00:47:34.672
see there's a significant, well, I should say, a

776
00:47:34.712 --> 00:47:36.652
substantial survival benefit

