00:47:37.512 --> 00:47:41.312
in favor of those patients who had a molecular response with greater than

778
00:47:41.452 --> 00:47:45.252
50% reduction in ctDNA and a hazard ratio of 0.41.

779
00:47:46.312 --> 00:47:49.672
So the message is that ctDNA is a more robust

780
00:47:49.712 --> 00:47:53.191
indicator of survival benefit than radiographic response.

781
00:47:55.232 --> 00:47:58.812
Now in the protocol, we did treat patients beyond

782
00:47:59.232 --> 00:48:00.592
radiographic progression,

783
00:48:01.612 --> 00:48:03.072
and these spider plots

