00:49:24.332 --> 00:49:27.792
Hazard ratio at that point was 0.61 for the adjusted

807
00:49:28.212 --> 00:49:28.872
analysis.

808
00:49:30.852 --> 00:49:31.672
So in conclusion,

809
00:49:32.642 --> 00:49:36.252
this study with tobentafusp is the longest follow-up for any bispecific

810
00:49:36.352 --> 00:49:40.322
T-cell engager in a solid tumor, and it's the first time that

811
00:49:40.392 --> 00:49:44.252
a five-year phase three analysis has been presented in metastatic uveal

812
00:49:44.292 --> 00:49:48.252
melanoma. It shows early and continued separation of the overall

813
00:49:48.332 --> 00:49:52.232
survival curves and a doubling of survival at the five-year time

814
00:49:52.272 --> 00:49:54.372
